1315Luxury Vinyl Tile</h2>

1316

1317<p>

1318Luxury Vinyl Tile, or LVT, is exceptionally durable and affordable. Its resistant to scratches, dents, and moisture, explaining its rise in popularity. It can mimic the look of real colors and textures in wood, stone, or tile. It requires little upkeep beyond the normal sweeping and cleaning. Browse our 2020 styles to find the best match for your home now.</p>

This flooring uses an interlocking design, so it doesnt have to be glued down.&nbsp;</p>

Like MaxAPEX, it dampens the sound of your footsteps, is waterproof, and extremely difficult to dent. This flooring uses an interlocking design for an easier installation compared to glued-down options.</p>
